Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:19.75,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Even though it hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:22.96,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…even though I feel sad…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:30.29,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…in the court I feel just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:38.49,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,When I hear the ball flying, my heart races.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:42.57,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Receive. Toss. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:47.56,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,One-two, one-two! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.36,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,But sometimes I cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:53.42,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,I'm a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:01:01.69,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Through the tears and sweat, putting up a youthful fight…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:09.83,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,…under the blue sky, I just want to scream:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:17.99,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.99,0:01:27.13,Default,Lyrics_English,0,0,0,,Attack! Attack! Number 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Episode 001\NFujimi Academy's new star
Comment: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to figure out these ellipses. Too many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,《Fujimi Academy》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you can't solve such a simple problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're such big shots for being here at Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakazawa-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even asked you a question yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What year are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.09,0:02:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh…, we're second year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Second year students, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still don't understand this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've mistaken you for juniors for a moment,\Nbut you really are second year students.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.49,0:02:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been listening to my class until now? Or maybe you've been sleeping all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Ayuhara here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,《Math》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun. Ayuhara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, get it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ikezaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is square root of 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I get it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She solved it in her sleep, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have read the example.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty bold in front of His Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked for your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you've just transferred, I won't allow such attitude. How dare you act like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If my class is so boring, go to the nurse office and sleep there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm going to the nurse office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She has some nerve acting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be friends with me, and that's why you followed me here?
Comment: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe comma not needed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Wind, take them to a peaceful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Receive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shoot!\N- Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, falling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes next serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to jump higher.\NOne more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Roger.\N- Let's give it our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ayuhara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Katsuragi-san, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You come to see us practice ever since transferring here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like volleyball?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You are interested, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But I also hate losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate losing…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she making fun of us? Did she just call us losers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nakazawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a compact you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you put on makeup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome our heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My. Why are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- We were waiting for you.\N- Kozue-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable. Take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need anything from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you stuck it to His Majesty was splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This. Debu and I couldn't believe our ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so brave, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, you've become the heroine of our useless student group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless students?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically we're the kind of students who don't fit in at the prestigious Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Ayuhara-san? \NWanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to be friends. \NWe could achieve something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Ike-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We could use your help, Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's decided. We're friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm…. What kind of friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- No big deal.\N- We'll only play around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we exactly do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For example…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,…this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just sit there. Dance with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like this. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you've got some nice moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hang out with the others, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The rest of the class are only goody-goodies after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we learned you told someone what we are doing here, we'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me, show me…, show me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is bad. Party's over.\N- Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're pretty famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ichinose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kashiwagi-kun was here just a moment ago, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What were they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And other things too….
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you feeling well, Ichinose-san?\N- Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hang out with these girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They treat me way better than you do, mister detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You serve as student council vice president, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me make myself clear: I hate Fujimi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Some school I've transferred into.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes to Fujimi Academy. You trouble us with your behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ken!\N- Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- How do you know Ken?\N- How do you know Ken?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-san is my nephew. Kozue is my niece, on my husband's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- What? This means—\N- We're actually related.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pretty shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find shells like that anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you expect to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The sounds of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I stayed at home in Tokyo, mama taught me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,…if you put your ear near a sea shell, you can hear the sound of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I'm at sea, maybe it could work the other way around, and I could hear Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking that, but there's no way that'd work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you transferred in the middle of the school term?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can return to Tokyo some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Home is where you make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you stay away from that useless bunch, you'll make many friends in no time.
Comment: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-kun, you just don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love the waves so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a long, long time, they eventually wear down their obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Waves are remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why are you skipping classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really want to skip them, but… motivation just doesn't seem to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When I don't have a goal, I don't feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What are you studying for, Tsutomu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you become vice president?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you seem so absent-minded?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Fuji looks so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't this clear for a while now. It's refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How curious…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,《Teachers room》
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,By Meihou Academy do you mean that prestigious institute in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's why I've had high expectations for having Ayuhara-san transfer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad call. She doesn't even come to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, professor Hongou?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Simply put, she does whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think we should chase every student and tell them what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I won't allow such misconduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This school has its rules for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna hang out after school? I need to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She hangs out with the other delinquents already.
Comment: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,rewrite? dunno
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I pity them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that their grades are poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice way to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What they need is to vent their aggression, …
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,…but with our sports section being in such a sorry state—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Hongou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The focus of our school lies in academic achievements. Sports are marginal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I oppose this way of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- W-W-What?\N- Let's ease up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding Ayuhara Kozue, for the time being let's just observe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any of this. What did they say I talked with Tsutomu-kun about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They said you ratted us out and told him we were go-go dancing earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No one but you could have told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We have two witnesses. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being silly. Nobody had to tell him, Tsutomu-kun figured it out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop calling him Tsutomu "-kun".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known you'd want your hands all over Ichinose-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Me with Tsutomu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go again. So cheeky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. This isn't some yakuza movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Too slow, too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Endure it.\N- Why are you butting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right here. Ayuhara-san didn't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We jumped to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I jump to conclusions all the time too. Right, Tsutomu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san and Ichinose-san being related…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ike-chan, what's with your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinose-san grasped it earlier. Now I'll treasure it foreve—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsutomu-san looks like a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Super-handsome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehh? H-How?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting that aside…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems your go-go dance was discussed at today's faculty meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll end up getting in trouble if you don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse, vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachers and you are viewing us in a bad light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.12,0:17:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They assume anyone that is a little different to be a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end this prejudice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They assume everything they don't understand must be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If they tried it, they might have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Naka! Radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it, Tsutomu-san? Wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.68,0:18:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, you're our boss! Our chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.27,0:18:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you teach me to be like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. But yeah, I could show you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi-san asked us to find you. We've looked everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd love to have you join our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After yesterday's practice, she's sure you've got what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a chance. You should take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'd rather hang out with Kashiwagi-san than play volleyball with you guys.
Comment: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,dunno
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, that club is, well—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Ayuhara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only that I'm disappointed with your practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,See you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what I'll do if she joins our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so full of herself. What makes her so special anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so angry over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that our academy's sports section is in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the newspapers say we're falling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kozue-san is in the eye of the cyclone. Something's about to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hase-san and Hara-san told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You insulted the volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've ever insulted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not lying to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only spoken the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so full of yourself, for a transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, you seem to be confident about your volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We'll test you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to test me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's going to be rough, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara-san, receive the serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue. Don't stop serving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You little…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That was low!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to our captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Same goes to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to Ayuhara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Your delinquent bunch isn't welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I mistaken? Aren't you the garbage of Fujimi Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have complaints, let's hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cruel! Calling us delinquents…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We never did anything to your volleyball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ask the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone calls you garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- What the heck?\N- Calm down, Naka. His Majesty is watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.47,0:22:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got a problem, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not delinquents. We won't fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We can always compete in sports, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the "delinquents", the useless group…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,…will challenge you to a match and show you how to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.34,0:23:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know the rules of the volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,One month. One month is all I'm asking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, you'll see that I'm not all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting. Truly interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- No way we wouldn't.\N- I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, this is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reckless. We don't even know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do, Ayuhara-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it official.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:58.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After taking over the so-called "garbage of Fujimi Academy"…
Comment: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:01.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ayuhara Kozue should be the start of a new line
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.40,0:24:01.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,…and challenging the volleyball club, \NAyuhara Kozue…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:03.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,…immediately begins harsh training.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:06.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But she runs into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:11.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The useless group seems to be more interested in dancing than volleyball.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.01,0:24:14.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Soon enough two of them want to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:16.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't think of something…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.35,0:24:20.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,…Kozue will be forced to forfeit the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.23,0:24:22.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Kozue doesn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.93,0:24:27.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to the next episode.
